content: It's cute but it doesn't let you change keyboards back and forth between emoji and writing
replyContent: Dear Barbara, thank you for your purchase. You can switch back and forth very easily actually. To change to a regular keyboard, simply tap the globe key at the lower left corner. To switch to Dachmoji again, long press the space bar for one second and you will see a pop up window for you to choose a number of other keyboards.
